---- MODULE WindowLifecycle ----
\* Gossamer webview window lifecycle from creation to destruction. Controls show/hide/run/destroy transitions.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Uninitialized, Hidden, Visible, Running, Closed

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, guard_mode

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Uninitialized, Hidden, Visible, Running, Closed}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Uninitialized
    /\ guard_mode = 0

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Uninitialized -> Hidden (gossamer_create)
gossamer_create ==
    /\ state = Uninitialized
    /\ TRUE
    /\ state' = Hidden
    /\ guard_mode := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Hidden -> Visible (gossamer_show)
gossamer_show ==
    /\ state = Hidden
    /\ state' = Visible
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Visible -> Hidden (gossamer_hide)
gossamer_hide ==
    /\ state = Visible
    /\ guard_mode = 0
    /\ state' = Hidden
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Visible -> Running (gossamer_run)
gossamer_run ==
    /\ state = Visible
    /\ state' = Running
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Hidden -> Running (gossamer_run)
gossamer_run ==
    /\ state = Hidden
    /\ state' = Running
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Running -> Closed (window_closed)
window_closed ==
    /\ state = Running
    /\ state' = Closed
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Visible -> Closed (gossamer_request_close)
gossamer_request_close ==
    /\ state = Visible
    /\ guard_mode = 0
    /\ state' = Closed
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Transition: Closed -> Uninitialized (gossamer_destroy)
gossamer_destroy ==
    /\ state = Closed
    /\ state' = Uninitialized
    /\ UNCHANGED guard_mode

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ gossamer_create
    \/ gossamer_show
    \/ gossamer_hide
    \/ gossamer_run
    \/ gossamer_run
    \/ window_closed
    \/ gossamer_request_close
    \/ gossamer_destroy

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, guard_mode>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: GuardedWindowCannotClose (safety)
GuardedWindowCannotClose == []([][WindowGuard # Free => WindowLifecycle # Closed]_WindowLifecycle)

\* Property: RevokedTokenNeverChecked (safety)
RevokedTokenNeverChecked == []([][CapabilityToken = Revoked => UNCHANGED CapabilityToken]_CapabilityToken)

\* Property: WindowEventuallyRuns (liveness)
WindowEventuallyRuns == <>(<>(WindowLifecycle = Running))


====
